DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to compare the relative bioavailability of Moexipril HCl 15mg tablets (by Paddock Laboratories, Inc.) with that of UnivascÂ® 15mg tablets (by Schwarz Pharma) following a single oral dose (1 x 15mg tablet) in healthy, adult subjects under fasting conditions.
DOC.brief_title: A Relative Bioavailability Study of Moexipril HCl 15 mg Tablets Under Fasting Conditions
DOC.criteria: Good health as determined by lack of clinically significant abnormalities in health assessment performed at screening Positive test results for HIV or Hepatitis B or C History of allergy or sensitivity to Moexipril HCl or related drugs
